1. Display all the Suppliers with the same Status as the supplier, ‘Kiran’.

mysql>  SELECT SNAME FROM SUPPLIERS
    -> WHERE STATUS IN (SELECT STATUS FROM SUPPLIERS
    -> WHERE SNAME = 'Kiran');
+-------+
| SNAME |
+-------+
| Jay   |
| Kiran |
| Harry |
+-------+
3 rows in set (1.303 sec)

