6. Display the name of the Supplier who has sold the maximum Quantity (in one 
sale).   

mysql> SELECT SNAME , MAX(QTY) FROM SUPPLIERS
    -> JOIN supplier_parts_project S
    -> WHERE S.`S#` = SUPPLIERS.`S#`
    -> GROUP BY SNAME
    -> ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC  LIMIT 1;
+-------+----------+
| SNAME | MAX(QTY) |
+-------+----------+
| Jay   | 6200     |
+-------+----------+
1 row in set (0.012 sec)

